{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-index-page-js","path":"/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Great coffee with a conscience","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.501466275659824,"src":"/static/534958a2cee3bb524a0bae118f2a4219/097fa/home-jumbotron.jpg","srcSet":"/static/534958a2cee3bb524a0bae118f2a4219/89b9c/home-jumbotron.jpg 512w,\n/static/534958a2cee3bb524a0bae118f2a4219/26852/home-jumbotron.jpg 1024w,\n/static/534958a2cee3bb524a0bae118f2a4219/097fa/home-jumbotron.jpg 1920w","sizes":"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"}}},"heading":"Great coffee with a conscience","subheading":"Support sustainable farming while enjoying a cup","mainpitch":{"title":"Why Kaldi","description":"Kaldi is the coffee store for everyone who believes that great coffee shouldn't just taste good, it should do good too. We source all of our beans directly from small scale sustainable farmers and make sure part of the profits are reinvested in their communities.\n"},"description":"Kaldi is the ultimate spot for coffee lovers who want to learn about their java’s origin and support the farmers that grew it. We take coffee production, roasting and brewing seriously and we’re glad to pass that knowledge to anyone.","intro":{"blurbs":[{"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.25,"src":"/static/277733984de58dd6d27eed18b510250d/1a97c/coffee.png","srcSet":"/static/277733984de58dd6d27eed18b510250d/d32b9/coffee.png 60w,\n/static/277733984de58dd6d27eed18b510250d/d08e9/coffee.png 120w,\n/static/277733984de58dd6d27eed18b510250d/1a97c/coffee.png 240w","sizes":"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px"}}},"text":"We sell green and roasted coffee beans that are sourced directly from independent farmers and farm cooperatives. We’re proud to offer a variety of coffee beans grown with great care for the environment and local communities. Check our post or contact us directly for current availability.\n"},{"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.25,"src":"/static/ec437153a2bd67b99cd975bf10c03292/1a97c/coffee-gear.png","srcSet":"/static/ec437153a2bd67b99cd975bf10c03292/d32b9/coffee-gear.png 60w,\n/static/ec437153a2bd67b99cd975bf10c03292/d08e9/coffee-gear.png 120w,\n/static/ec437153a2bd67b99cd975bf10c03292/1a97c/coffee-gear.png 240w","sizes":"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px"}}},"text":"We offer a small, but carefully curated selection of brewing gear and tools for every taste and experience level. No matter if you roast your own beans or just bought your first french press, you’ll find a gadget to fall in love with in our shop.\n"},{"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.25,"src":"/static/7de80b5f57f779d116b3a186b9a9268e/1a97c/tutorials.png","srcSet":"/static/7de80b5f57f779d116b3a186b9a9268e/d32b9/tutorials.png 60w,\n/static/7de80b5f57f779d116b3a186b9a9268e/d08e9/tutorials.png 120w,\n/static/7de80b5f57f779d116b3a186b9a9268e/1a97c/tutorials.png 240w","sizes":"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px"}}},"text":"Love a great cup of coffee, but never knew how to make one? Bought a fancy new Chemex but have no clue how to use it? Don't worry, we’re here to help. You can schedule a custom 1-on-1 consultation with our baristas to learn anything you want to know about coffee roasting and brewing. Email us or call the store for details.\n"},{"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.25,"src":"/static/d2f97849ad334b9280651604a80a01a6/1a97c/meeting-space.png","srcSet":"/static/d2f97849ad334b9280651604a80a01a6/d32b9/meeting-space.png 60w,\n/static/d2f97849ad334b9280651604a80a01a6/d08e9/meeting-space.png 120w,\n/static/d2f97849ad334b9280651604a80a01a6/1a97c/meeting-space.png 240w","sizes":"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px"}}},"text":"We believe that good coffee has the power to bring people together. That’s why we decided to turn a corner of our shop into a cozy meeting space where you can hang out with fellow coffee lovers and learn about coffee making techniques. All of the artwork on display there is for sale. The full price you pay goes to the artist.\n"}],"heading":"What we offer","description":"Kaldi is the ultimate spot for coffee lovers who want to learn about their java’s origin and support the farmers that grew it. We take coffee production, roasting and brewing seriously and we’re glad to pass that knowledge to anyone. This is an edit via identity...\n"}}}},"pageContext":{"id":"d41c4783-c02a-51cd-bdd4-9038613d4f9b"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1606870023","4080856488"]}